    <p class="MTBtext">The Meant to be series (MTB for short) is the 2nd series I started.
        It starts in year 2 where the students are getting petrified and Harry and Ron are going to save Ginny.
        This series is based on the idea what would happen if Harry and Ginny got together around this time.
        There aren't big changes compared to the original story at the beginning, they come later on.
        This is also known as my cuteness series, ATW is my action series.</p>
    <iframe width="392" height="221" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ULKYogsx4cI" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen class="mtbvid"></iframe>
