    <p class="SHtext">Star Hamilton is my character I play as when I roleplay.
        It's not related to me in real life at all luckily.
        It's a very dark and depressing story, the start sets a point on what kind of dark things that happen later on.
        It's about Star Hamilton who ends up the last of his family at a young age, he only has Edward his family phoenix left.
        His past haunts him in many ways, but Edward and some people help him even when he's very introverted
        The series is very depressing, but later on it gets better and happier, with some happy moments in between.
        This is my most unique series, but other characters we know like Ginny will show up when Star goes to Hogwarts.</p>
